Add a contact to the watchlist

Usage: mxr cadence watch [OPTIONS] <EMAIL>

Arguments:
  <EMAIL>

Options:
      --account <ACCOUNT>
      --expected-days <EXPECTED_DAYS>
      --note <NOTE>
      --allow-list-sender              Watch the contact even if it looks like a list sender
  -h, --help                           Print help
